data.description: This stunning 1,800 sq ft property in the highly sought after neighborhood of Randle Heights is just waiting for its new owner. The kitchen is modern and updated, featuring granite countertops and stainless steel appliances.  A well-appointed kitchen that is a significant feature for a home. The property boasts a large backyard with a patio, which can be a valuable outdoor space for relaxation and entertainment. The living room is equipped with a bay window, which brings in  natural light and adds charm to the space. The dining room features decorative mirrors, beautiful hardwood floors and recessed lighting creating a stylish and well-lit dining area. The lower level is equipped with a half bath, and washer/dryer. A fenced yard and patio adorns the large backyard space. *************Newly Updated basement and bathroom, new kitchen tile, new paint on all levels, and brand NEW ROOF**************** ALL OFFERS ARE DUE BY 11/21/2023
